default2.1 How do Government and local authorities identify demand?default 
default2.2 These comments relate to the situation in Wales
default. The variation in research is huge. The Welsh Government carries out an annual National Transport Survey. Public transport users in rural areas are rarely asked directly for their view by officials. Local authorities have widely different priorities.
